productReviews.reviewText: I saw one of these in The Gambia and I bought one.
This Awesome works outstandingly well. It beautifully improves my basketball by a lot.
I tried to impale it but got fudge all over it.
My neighbor Montserrat has one of these. She works as a circus performer and she says it looks shriveled.
one of my hobbies is skateboarding. and when i'm skateboarding this works great.
